overview: An OUTRAGEOUS-RAW comedy about a group of friends lead by comedian Do-Do Brown (from BET Comicview, Lil Zane's video "Callin Me") Whom by the way have no job; no sence; and not a worry in the world. They decide to show Atlanta how raw they can be, which is why the title speaks for itself "Hell 2 the Naw." The only things these guys have going for them are their girlfriends- led by Tracy Johnson, (Big Ain't Bad) who is as raw as the guys.
title: Hell 2 the Naw
